    <h2>We all want glowy, glassy skin with texture like a glazed donut. And chances are, you’ve heard about, tested, or are currently using beauty’s most beloved molecular powerhouse, vitamin C.</h2>
    <p>Our bodies need vitamin C on a daily basis. Since we can’t create it on our own, we have to get it elsewhere (think fruits, veggies, and wellness supplements). Applying topical vitamin C in your daily skincare routine touts a long list of positives cheered by derms + pros.&nbsp;<strong>Let's break down our favorite 5.</strong></p>
    
    </div>
    
    
